{
  "stem": "268.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So what I remember distinctly is she caught  my eye-- beautiful girl, beautiful dark eyes, dark hair, pigtails, gosh, complexion like peach and cream.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I said, oh gosh, what a beau-- this is god's greatest creation here.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I says, what's you name, come on down.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So she says, [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Yahzhah. ?] And I told her my name.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I said, I got to remember that name.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So, finally, after about a half a hour, another guy joins.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So they came down.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We talked, and so I introduced myself, and I told them my name.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we told, we said, we should get together sometimes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we talked a little more about what school and what grade are you in.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Turned out they were younger than I was, by two years, and some of them three years.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that was-- that's what I remember about services.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I do remember the girl.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, of course, later on I start looking for her.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I found her in the ghetto, and we struck up a friendship.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I, perhaps, will talk a little later on about that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But, in meantime, I would like to answer your question about the ghetto life and what I remember about the first services.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This was-- it really stands out in my mind.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The first High Holiday service in what was then already beginning to be a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I'll still-- coming back to my work, this is what I did the first, perhaps, year.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Then they drafted me into a factory, into a ceramic factor-- actually my dad, too, and my brother.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they took about 30 or 40 of us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we worked-- there I spend about two years, two, perhaps, two and 1/2 years, in the ceramic factory.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
